<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In Zend_Controller_Request_Http, allow the various get*() methods to return a specified default value:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
public function getQuery($key = null, $default = null)
{
    if (null === $key) {
        return $_GET;
    }
    return (isset($_GET[$key])) ? $_GET[$key] : $default;
}
</code></pre>

